msgid "Get a practical introduction to Quarkus, the full-stack framework for building cloud-native Java applications, by <a href=\"https://developers.redhat.com/e-books/quarkus-action?extIdCarryOver=true&sc_cid=701f2000001Css0AAC\" alt=\"Quarkus in Action free download link\">downloading a free copy of “Quarkus in Action”</a> by <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/martin-stefanko/\" target=\"_blank\">Martin Štefanko</a> and <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/janmartiska/\" target=\"_blank\">Jan Martiška</a>."
